        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses adaptations in flowers and their heritability.</p> 
<p>Mentions advertisements for HS’s book [? <hi rend="italic">Study of sociology</hi> (1873)].</p> 
            <p>Thought HS would have profited by principle that a character appearing late in life is inherited at same age.</p>
